@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
@-moz-document domain(boards.4chan.org),domain(rs.4chan.org),domain(sys.4chan.org)
{
/* AGENT_SHEET */
    *
    {
        font-family: Palatino Linotype !important ;
    }
    body
    {
        background-color: #191516!important;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        background-image:url(data:image/jpeg;base64,) !important;
        background-position: bottom right !important;
        background-repeat:no-repeat !important ;
        background-attachment:fixed !important ;
    }
    hr
    {
        visibility:collapse !important;
    }
    a
    {
        font-size:13px!important ;
        color:#7d6004 !important ;
        text-decoration:none !important ;
        font-weight:normal !important ;
        
    }
    a:hover
    {
       font-weight:normal !important ;
       text-decoration:underline !important ;
    }
    span.name, span.postertrip, div.sideArrows, div.absBotText, div.stylechanger
    {
        display:none !important  ;
    }
    a[href="javascript:;"]
    {
        text-decoration:none !important ;
    }
    div.deleteform
    {
        display:none!important  ;
    }

    /*Start PostArea*/
    table.postForm
    {
        overflow: hidden !important;
        border-spacing:0 !important;
        background-color: #3c1518 !important ;
        vertical-align:top!important;
        font-size:10px !important ;
        position: fixed!important; 
        right: -395px!important; 
        top:6%!important; 
        margin-left: 100%!important; 
        margin-right: 0%!important; 
        width: 300px!important; 
        opacity:.2 !important ; 
        z-index:1 !important;
    }
    
    table.postForm td
    {
        background-color: #3c1518 !important ;
        font:13px Palatino Linotype !important ;
        border:none!important;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
    }
    table.postForm:hover
    {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        right: -7px!important
    }
    
    table.postForm input
    {
        width: 300px!important
    }
    table.postForm INPUT[name="spoiler"] 
    {
        height: 10px !important; 
        width: 10px !important}
    table.postForm INPUT[name="sub"] + INPUT[value="Post"] 
    {
        height: 24px!important; 
        width: 55px !important;
        line-height: 10px!important;
        padding: 0px !important;
        vertical-align: top!important
    }
    table.postForm div#captchaContainer
    {
     display:none!important  ;
    }
    
 
    table#recaptcha_table
    {
        width: 300px !important
    }
    a#recaptcha_reload_btn
    {
        position: absolute !important; 
        top: 245px !important;
        right: 33px !important; 
        opacity: .8 !important;
        width: 0% !important; 
        overflow: visible !important;
    }
    table#recaptcha_table td,.recaptcha_input_area
    {
        padding: 0px !important;
        padding-top: 0px !important;
        padding-bottom: 0px !important
    }
    
    table.postForm textarea  
    {
        width: 300px!important
    }
    
    
    tr.rules, img#recaptcha_switch_audio, img#recaptcha_whatsthis,
    img#recaptcha_logo, img#recaptcha_tagline, table.postForm input#postPassword + span
    {
        display:none!important  ;
    }

/*END PostArea*/
    /*START Replace Picture*/
    img#recaptcha_reload
    { 
        height: 0px !important;
        padding-top: 18px !important;
        width: 25px !important;
        background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;
    }
    
    [src$="closed.gif"]
    {
        height: 0px !important;
        padding-top: 18px !important;
        width: 18px !important;
        background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;
    }
    [src$="sticky.gif"]
    {
        height: 0px !important;
        padding-top: 18px !important;
        width: 18px !important;
        background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;
    }
    [src$="stop.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    
    [src$="arrow_down2.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    [src$="arrow_down.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    [src$="arrow_left.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    [src$="arrow_right.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABIAAAASCAYAAABWzo5XAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB9sCGwAABTmfMT0AAABdSURBVDjLY2AYbIARmcPPE0uS5o9fFmMaxM8Ty5Aoc/4/KQbNf2LICDOMCZciLYWvDFoKX4k2lIlaYcSCS+LaA264y5D5A+ciUl1GPxcNnjAi1iX0T0d0z7SDDwAAKvYg5eHxVIkAAAAASUVORK5CYII=)!important;}
    [src$="arrow_up.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABIAAAASCAYAAABWzo5XAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB9sCGwAAORbwTboAAABMSURBVDjLY2AYtoARmVOgofOfFM0TblyB62eilovoZ5CWwlcGLYWv9HMRCz6XMDAwMFx7wI2VTz8X4bKZkMto5yJcYUBIfvAlyGEMADOxF9/bnBYhAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC)!important;}
    [src$="ban.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABIAAAASCAYAAABWzo5XAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB9sCGwADHpjXqxIAAABXSURBVDjLY2AYbIARmcPPE0uS5o9fFmMaxM8Ty5Aoc/4/KQbNf2LICDOMBV1SS+ErXs3XHnBjFWeiVhixkGozzMXo8rR3Ea6wGg2jwRhGuGykW6YdfAAAxwohaXj+94cAAAAASUVORK5CYII=)!important;}
    [src$="cross.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    [src$="empty.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    [src$="post_expand_minus.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABIAAAASCAYAAABWzo5XAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB9sCGwAGEuwWE3wAAABNSURBVDjLY2AYbIARmcPPE0uS5o9fFmMaxM8Ty5Aoc/4/KQbNf2LICDOMiVpeG8YGsaALaCl8JUrjtQfcdHIRuk2jsUY9g6iWaQcfAAD7cBHfD7iOwQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==)!important;}
    [src$="post_expand_plus.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABIAAAASCAYAAABWzo5XAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAAZiS0dEAP8A/wD/oL2nkwAAAAlwSFlzAAALEwAACxMBAJqcGAAAAAd0SU1FB9sCGhc0Ar0EhfkAAABeSURBVDjLY2AYbIARmcPPE0uS5o9fFmMaxM8Ty5Aoc/4/KQbNf2LICDOMiZBiLYWvDFoKXwkaykStMBp8BrFgCxNcYYUMrj3gppOL0G2CuQRdfCTHGqEwo3mmHXwAABiCGl++yebeAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC)!important;}
    [src$="post_expand_rotate.gif"]{background-image:url(data:image/gif;base64,)!important;}
    [src$="quote.png"]{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)!important;}
    /*END Replace Picture*/
    
    div.postContainer.opContainer
    {
    max-width:80% !important ;
     word-wrap:break-word;
    }
    
    div.post.reply
    {
        border-radius:8px !important ;
        background-color: #3c1518 !important ;
        max-width:950px !important ;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        border:none !important ;
        font-size:13px!important;
        word-wrap:break-word;
    }
    div.post.reply:target
    {
        background-color: #612025 !important ;
        color: #ba4420 !important ;
    }
    a.summary.desktop,div.postContainer.replyContainer
    {
        clear: both !important;
		padding-left: 20px !important;
		display: block !important;
    }
    div#globalMessage
    {
        max-width:95% !important ;
        color: #ba4420 !important ;
    }
    span.abbr
    {
       color: #9a4821 !important ; 
    }
    div#boardNavDesktop
    {
        max-width:95% !important ;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        font-size:13px!important ;
        
    }
    div.pages.cataloglink
    {
        border:solid !important ;
        border-width: thin !important ; 
        border-color: #3c1518 !important ; 
        text-align: center !important ;  
        padding: 2px !important ; 
    }
    div.desktop
    {
         max-width:80% !important ;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        font-size:13px!important ;
    }
    div.pagelist, div.reply.dialog
    {
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        background-color: #191516!important;
        border:none!important;
    }
    div.pages>strong, span.fileText, span.subject
    {
        color: #b8441d !important;
    }
    
    div.postingMode
    {
    background-color: #3c1518 !important;
     color: #b8441d !important;
    }
    
    td.postblock
    { 
        background-color: #3c1518 !important ;
        color:#b8441d !important;
        border:none!important;
    }
    td.subject
    {
     color: inherit !important;
    }
    tr.highlightPost
    {
        background-color: inherit !important ;
    }
    table.flashListing tr:nth-of-type(2n+1)
    { 
        background-color: #3c1518 !important ;
        color:#b8441d !important;
        border:none!important;
    }

    /*START Buttons*/
    input, input[type="submit"], input[type="button"],input[type="checkbox"], select, textarea
    {
        -moz-appearance: none!important;
        -webkit-appearance: none!important;
        background-color: #191516!important;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        border: .5px #3c1518 solid !important;
    }
    input[type="submit"]:hover, input[type="button"]:hover,input[type="checkbox"]:hover, select:hover, button:hover
    { 
        box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 10px #9a4821 ;
        -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 10px #9a4821 ;
    }
    input[type="checkbox"]
    {
        border: .5px #9a4821 solid !important;
    }
    /*END Buttons*/
}


/*REPORT*/

@-moz-document domain(sys.4chan.org)
{
    body
    {
        background-color: #191516!important;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        background-position: bottom right !important;
        background-image:none !important;
        background-repeat:no-repeat !important ;
        background-attachment:fixed !important ;
    }
    div.rules,img#recaptcha_whatsthis,img#recaptcha_switch_audio,img#recaptcha_logo,img#recaptcha_tagline

    {
        display:none !important;
    }
    input, input[type="submit"], input[type="button"], input[type="radio"], select, button, textarea
    {
        -moz-appearance: none!important;
        -webkit-appearance: none!important;
        border: 0 !important;
        background-color: #191516!important;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        border: 2px #3c1518 solid !important;
    }
    fieldset
    {
        border: 2px #3c1518 solid !important;
    } 
}


/*Rapidshare*/
@-moz-document domain(rs.4chan.org)
{
 
    center>table>tbody>tr>td>table
    {
       display:inline!important;
    }
    span
    {
        color:#b8441d !important;
    }
    span#navtop
    {
        max-width:95% !important ;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        font-size:13px!important ;
    
    }
    table.pages
    {
        background-color: #191516!important;
        border:none!important;
    }
    table.pages>tbody>tr>td
    {
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
    }
    span#navbot
    {
        float:none !important ;
        max-width:95% !important ;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        font-size:13px !important ;
    }

    div#footer>center
    {
        color: #2a4821 !important ;
        clear:none !important ;
        margin: 0px !important;
        padding:0px !important;
	}
	body>table>tbody>tr>td>table>tbody>tr>td+td
	{
	   display:none !important;
	}
}
/*framenav*/
@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.4chan.org/framesnav"),url-prefix("https://www.4chan.org/framesnav")
{
    body
    {
        font:11.5px Palatino Linotype !important ;
        background-color: #f9cc91 !important;
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
        overflow:hidden!important ;
        background-image:none  !important ;
    }
    ul
    {
        line-height:120% !important ;
    }
    a
    {
        color: #9a4821 !important ;
    }
    h2
    {
        background-color: #2e0e0f !important;
        border-radius:2% !important ;
        text-align:center !important ;
        width:100% !important ;
    }
    div#logo,div#dis,div#draw,span.plus,div#logo+ul+h2,div#img+h2,div#up+h2,div#up+h2+ul
    {
        display:none !important ;
    }
}

/*** FRONTPAGE ***/

@-moz-document url(http://www.4chan.org/),url(https://www.4chan.org/){

#hd, #close-announce,div[id="ft"]
  { display: none !important;}

/* sets font */
  body, span#navtop, td.replyhl, td.reply, a, a:hover, a.quotejs, a.quotejs:hover, a.quotelink, span.filesize
  {
    font:13px Palatino Linotype !important ;

  } 

  html,body
  {
    background-color: #191516!important;
    color: #9a4821 !important ;
    background-image:url(data:image/jpeg;base64,) !important;
    background-position: bottom right !important;
    background-repeat:no-repeat !important ;
    background-attachment:fixed !important ;
font-weight:bolder!important;
font-size:13px!important;
  }

/*Color Changes*/
  b,font.unkfunc, th>font,a
  {
      color: #9a4821 !important ;
    text-decoration:none !important ;
  }
  tr>th
  {
    background-color: #3c1518 !important;
  }
.boxbar, #preview-tooltip-nws H2, #preview-tooltip-ws H2

  {  background: #3c1518 !important; 

    text-align: center !important;

    color: #9a4821 !important ;


   
}
#filter-button, #option-button

  { background: #3c1518 !important; 


    color: #9a4821 !important ;
letter-spacing: 0px !important;

    padding : 0px !important;

    margin: 0 !important; 

text-transform:capitalize!important; 
font-weight:bold!important; 

 }

.box-outer, #preview-tooltip-nws, #preview-tooltip-ws
{
    background-color: #f9cc91 !important; 
    border:none !important;
    color: #9a4821 !important ;
    border-style:solid !important ;
    border-width:1px !important ;
}
#preview-tooltip-nws, #preview-tooltip-ws
{
    border-width:2px !important ;
}
 .p_postername,.postertrip
{
    display:none!important;
}
.p_filetitle
{
    color: #b8441d !important;
}
div[class="yui-u first"],div[class="boxcontent"]>ul>li
{
    background-color: transparent!important; 
}
.yui-menu-shadow
{ 
    display: none !important;
}
.yuimenuitem,.yui-skin-sam .yuimenu .bd
{
    background-color: #3c1518 !important; 
    border:none !important;
    color: #9a4821 !important ;
}

ul
{
    border:none !important;
}
.column
{ 
    text-align: center !important;
    text-transform: capitalize!important;
    color: #9a4821 !important; 
}


.column > H3
{
    color: #9a4821 !important;
    font-weight:bolder!important;
    font-size:13px!important;
}

#disclaimer-dialog_mask
{ 
    opacity: .5 !important;
    background: #3c1518 !important;
}
#disclaimer-dialog .ft
{ 
    text-align: center !important;
}
#disclaimer-dialog .hd
{
    background-color: #f9cc91 !important; 
    border:none !important;
    color: #9a4821 !important ;
}

#disclaimer-dialog
{
    text-align: center !important;
    background-color: #3c1518 !important; 
    border:none !important;
    color: #9a4821 !important ;
}

#disclaimer-dialog BUTTON
{
    -moz-appearance: none!important;
    -webkit-appearance: none!important;  
    background-color: #191516!important;
    color: #9a4821 !important ;
    border: .5px #3c1518 solid !important;
}
#disclaimer-dialog BUTTON:hover
{ 
    box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 10px #9a4821 ;

}
